{"tid":867071,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"劈價蔓延，中半山花園台減至上年價成交","createTime":"2018-10-18T11:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T07:28:05.000Z","uid":159798,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"79c4978ee532dec34a8af17bd6c9f7e26e0faea4","tid":867071,"uid":159798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:06:56.000Z","msg":"市況回調，豪宅盤亦減價出售。市場消息指出，中半山花園台3座中高層B室海景戶，實用面積2,828方呎，原以1.25億元放售，近日減至約1億元售出，減幅約兩成，呎價約35,361元。<br />\n<br />\n區內代理透露，屋苑該座數一向較少成交，對上一宗成交為於去年一個高層A室，以9,920萬元沽出，呎價35,078元，故是次成交價重返去年價錢。"},{"pid":"e82b85797007df6b2e567a56bc6a461e9cdb566b","tid":867071,"uid":10635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:07:36.000Z","msg":"豪宅咁離地， 唔計！！"},{"pid":"b7e42c8dba9e5bb22137f5aaf344a821a53c2040","tid":867071,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e82b85797007df6b2e567a56bc6a461e9cdb566b","tid":867071,"uid":10635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:07:36.000Z","msg":"豪宅咁離地， 唔計！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:08:05.000Z","msg":"跌，唔計"},{"pid":"6ab5cdd1d4e7fe510ba8be617ad52d7f0c50b0b7","tid":867071,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:08:20.000Z","msg":"唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e0bca18ae76134e847fad53886f367c12c2fbc","tid":867071,"uid":193364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:10:18.000Z","msg":"豪宅唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd98ba617ef2e819244aa689298f4fc6b7cf640","tid":867071,"uid":58046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:11:21.000Z","msg":"唔計"},{"pid":"0671dd797f66346b8197e4480b0e0ddde1b4185f","tid":867071,"uid":159798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:17:52.000Z","msg":"劈到去港島，CCL會扣好多血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c12a3a32129ca1a6aba3d0